id: 2659
name: Stamps
power: 1
text: |
  Stamps are a category of asset ownable by players . The
  Collector is an office. The Collector tracks Stamps in eir weekly
  report.

  For each person there is a corresponding type of stamp.

  Any player CAN, once per week, pay X Stamps, where each specified
  Stamp is a different type, to increase eir own score by (X^2)-X
  points.

  Any player CAN, once per week, pay X Stamps, where each Stamp is
  the same type, to increase eir own score by (X-1)*2 points.

  Any player CAN win by paying N Stamps, where N is the current
  number of active players and each specified Stamp is of a
  different type.
